stateDiagram-v2
    %% What You Missed Preview (US2) - State Diagram

    [*] --> HIDDEN : channel opened, no unread

    [*] --> COMPACT : channel opened, unread > 0

    COMPACT --> LOADING : user clicks expand
    LOADING --> EXPANDED : preview fetched from backend
    LOADING --> ERROR : API error
    ERROR --> LOADING : retry
    EXPANDED --> COMPACT : user collapses

    COMPACT --> DISMISSED : user dismisses
    EXPANDED --> DISMISSED : user dismisses

    DISMISSED --> [*] : markChannelAsRead()

    note right of COMPACT
        Shows unread count badge
        No backend call yet
    end note

    note right of LOADING
        GET /api/summaries/preview
        Spinner displayed
    end note

    note right of EXPANDED
        Displays one-line preview
        from SummarizationProvider
    end note
